  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_36_1479-1548",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "1479-1548",
      "markText": "当她已准备停当，在临走前的最后一刻，我总要最后再问她一次是不是真不想陪我去，这倒并不是我怀疑她的回答，而是为了让她不怀疑自己有自主的自由。",
      "totalCount": 5810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1479&rangeEnd=1548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1479&rangeEnd=1548"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_35_743-760",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "743-760",
      "markText": "人越是不计较幸福，就越是感到幸福。",
      "totalCount": 5161,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=743&rangeEnd=760",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=743&rangeEnd=760"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_48_3277-3364",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "3277-3364",
      "markText": "原来我还觉得莫名其妙，现在已经真相大白了；过去我无缘无故地受到鄙视，而今我有充分的理由来鄙视他人了；埃米丽亚的一切神秘的举动现在都可以用“私通”这种极其简单的词来加以解释了。",
      "totalCount": 2704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=3277&rangeEnd=3364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=3277&rangeEnd=3364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_37_1877-1939",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1877-1939",
      "markText": "那些日子里我是那么失望，甚至抱怨起埃米丽亚来。从某种程度上来说，正是因为她那么热衷于置家，我才被迫迈出这么草率和危险的一步。",
      "totalCount": 2688,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1877&rangeEnd=1939",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1877&rangeEnd=1939"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_37_5562-5624",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "5562-5624",
      "markText": "与此同时，我对埃米丽亚的爱变得前所未有的强烈，有时候，我甚至十分内疚，责备自己曾把她想得很坏，认为她是个自私而又冷漠的女人。",
      "totalCount": 2013,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=5562&rangeEnd=5624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=5562&rangeEnd=5624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_37_3312-3365",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "3312-3365",
      "markText": "我心事重重、一筹莫展，却看到她这么泰然而又心满意足的样子，就越发觉得她这样未免太自私，至少是太无动于衷了。",
      "totalCount": 1974,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3312&rangeEnd=3365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3312&rangeEnd=3365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_37_1625-1652",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1625-1652",
      "markText": "一想到我迟早得设法满足她的愿望，我心里就感到十分惆怅。",
      "totalCount": 1854,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39745544&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1625&rangeEnd=1652",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cac323d0725e7808cacd0b1?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1625&rangeEnd=1652"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39745544_40_4522-4583",
